name: Becquerel-org.github.io
body:
### Project Becquerel
This used to be a private git host for several people, but it's all moved to GitHub now. If you find some of your repositories in the org listing to the left, please ping Magnus (@jyujin) to have them moved to your own GitHub account.

To see all the projects, go to https://github.com/becquerel-org and have a browse.

### Kyuba

If you came looking for the old kyuba.org content, there is an archive over at my blog: http://ef.gy/kyuba
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
